&lt;p&gt;解耦： 解耦意味着减少组件之间及其所使用数据类型之间的依赖关系。进而提升程序的正确性、质量及可维护性。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>interface</title><link>https://foreverool.github.io/notes/golang-notes/hand-on-go-programming/interfaces/</link><pubDate>Fri, 23 Jan 2026 23:35:18 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://foreverool.github.io/notes/golang-notes/hand-on-go-programming/interfaces/</guid><description>&lt;div class="note-card "&gt;
